parameters.content:
## Add Car – Post
 workflow to add cars to the database table.      I cleaned the information in Set and put in the Excel.

## Upgrade Car´s data – patch
 workflow to Upgrade car´s information in the database table.

## Delete Cars – Delete
 workflow to delete cars from the database table.

## Sold Cars -Patch
 workflow to delete sold cars from the inventory database table ad move them to the sold database table.

## Return Cars-Patch
 workflow to delete returned cars from the sold database table ad move them to the  inventory database table.

## Get stock Cars - Get
 workflow to get all the available cars from the inventoey database table

## API REST - ARMAZEM AUTO WEB

Add Car - POST : https://n8n-n8n.sjw220.easypanel.host/webhook/ACBE

Upgrade Car - Patch: https://n8n-n8n.sjw220.easypanel.host/webhook/AC_ACTUALIZAR_STOCK

Delete Cars - Delete: https://n8n-n8n.sjw220.easypanel.host/webhook/AC_STOCK_DELETE

Sold Cars - Patch: https://n8n-n8n.sjw220.easypanel.host/webhook/AC_VENDIDO

Returned Cars- Patch: https://n8n-n8n.sjw220.easypanel.host/webhook/AC_NO_VENDIDO

Get All the Cars- Get: https://n8n-n8n.sjw220.easypanel.host/webhook/AC_READ_STOCK

## OBSERVATIONS:

This API REST is made for an base44 web aplication  to control an Car Dealer´s Stock

Web App: https://app-989ea33a-7e3c-4894-921a-01cf869d7229.base44.app
